    <item>
      <title>由于能源部门业绩不佳，信实工业利润未达预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/reliance-misses-profit-estimate-on-poor-show-by-energy-units</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁穆克什·安巴尼 (Mukesh Ambani) 控制的信实工业有限公司 (Reliance Industries Ltd.) 报告的利润再次低于分析师的预期，因为其核心炼油业务的利润率较低，抵消了电信资费上调带来的好处。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/reliance-misses-profit-estimate-on-poor-show-by-energy-units</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 13:36:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
